FBIS4-62840 "drsov097ap_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-097 Daily Report 19 May 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Preparations for U.S.-Russian Exercises Halted Preparations for U.S.-Russian Exercises Halted LD1905100094 Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy in Russian 0800 GMT 19 May 94 LD1905100094 Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy Russian BFN [Text] The Russian Defense Ministry has halted preparations for exercises at Totskoye training ground. New talks will be held in June with the Pentagon on the peacekeeping forces' joint exercises. The Defense Ministry informed the Russian State Duma's defense committee of this. It is particularly noted that President Yeltsin agrees with the Duma's position on the need to cancel these exercises.
